Instructions:

-> Use the w,s,a,d keys to move around in the world.
-> f- First person cam mode toggle
-> t- Third person cam mode toggle
-> y- Tower cam mode toggle
-> j- Jump
-> b- Tile/block view toggle. Use the arrow key to move to different tiles.
-> h- Helicopter view. Move the mouse to move the helicopter. To change the viewing angle move the mouse with left mouse botton pressed and scroll	can to used to zoom in at zoom out.


Credits:

-> The header files md2model, vec3f and imageloader, and a md2 model for the robot, from www.videotutorialsrock.com are modified and used for the 	game as per the terms in (i).
-> The code for GLMSolidCube function as used in the world.cpp file is a modification of the GLSolidCube function obtained from the official
	OpenGl documentation.


